PN,31401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776269466
OL,3,CEx Nato chief says UK is
OL,4,C'underprepared, underinsured and under
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FThe prime minister has left the UK
OL,8,Funprepared for war due to an "ever-
OL,9,Fexpanding welfare budget" and
OL,10,F"corrosive complacency", the former
OL,11,FNato chief Lord George Robertson has
OL,12,Fwarned.
OL,14,FThe former Labour defence secretary
OL,15,Fwill use a speech on Tuesday evening
OL,16,Fto accuse ministers of being unwilling
OL,17,Fto make the necessary investment to
OL,18,Fsecure the UK's defence capabilities
OL,19,Fin the years to come.
OL,26,@pD@^OUqD@YO]rD@AOUrD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776269466
OL,3,CEx Nato chief says UK is
OL,4,C'underprepared, underinsured and under
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FIn the speech, he will say: "We are
OL,8,Funderprepared. We are underinsured. We
OL,9,Fare under attack. We are not safe...
OL,10,FBritain's national security and safety
OL,11,Fis in peril."
OL,13,FLord Robertson authored the Strategic
OL,14,FDefence Review last year, a ten-year
OL,15,Fplan of what is required to meet the
OL,16,Fchanging military and defence
OL,17,Frequirements in the current climate.
OL,26,@oD@]OUsD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776269466
OL,3,CEx Nato chief says UK is
OL,4,C'underprepared, underinsured and under
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FThe government has since delayed the
OL,8,Fpublication of the Defence Investment
OL,9,FPlan, setting out the money allocated
OL,10,Fto achieve the recommendations made in
OL,11,FLord Robertson's review.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
