OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776269466
OL,3,CEx Nato chief says UK is
OL,4,C'underprepared, underinsured and under
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FLord Robertson told the Financial
OL,8,FTimes there was a gap between the
OL,9,Fprime minister's rhetoric on defence
OL,10,Fand the action he had delivered,
OL,11,Fsaying the PM was "not willing to make
OL,12,Fthe necessary investment".
OL,14,FHe will accuse "non-military experts
OL,15,Fin the Treasury" of "vandalism",
OL,16,Faccording to extracts of his speech
OL,17,Fpublished by the newspaper.
OL,26,@sD@SOUtD@YO]vD@POUwD@PO]wD@UOUwD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776269466
OL,3,CEx Nato chief says UK is
OL,4,C'underprepared, underinsured and under
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FHe will say: "We cannot defend Britain
OL,8,Fwith an ever-expanding welfare
OL,9,Fbudget," and accuse Labour of a
OL,10,F"corrosive complacency today in
OL,11,FBritain's political leadership".
OL,13,FContinuing, he is set to say: "Lip
OL,14,Fservice is paid to the risks, the
OL,15,Fthreats, the bright red signals of
OL,16,Fdanger ` but even a promised national
OL,17,Fconversation about defence can't be
OL,18,Fstarted."
OL,26,@oD@NOUrD@AOUuD@_OUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776269466
OL,3,CEx Nato chief says UK is
OL,4,C'underprepared, underinsured and under
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FLord Robertson's defence review, which
OL,8,Fwas published in June last year,
OL,9,Fadvocated for a Nato-centric approach
OL,10,Fto the UK's future military investment.
OL,12,FReferencing US President Donald
OL,13,FTrump's criticism of the defence
OL,14,Falliance, Robertson said: "Recent days
OL,15,Fhave shown that the role and
OL,16,Fpriorities of the United States have
OL,17,Fshifted, and will never be the same
OL,18,Fagain."
OL,26,@vD@[OUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776269466
OL,3,CEx Nato chief says UK is
OL,4,C'underprepared, underinsured and under
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FThe government has committed to spend
OL,8,F2.5% of gross domestic product on
OL,9,Fdefence by 2027, increasing to 3% in
OL,10,Fthe next parliament and a Nato-agreed
OL,11,Ftarget of 3.5% by 2035.
OL,13,FStarmer told MPs on Monday that the
OL,14,Fgovernment is working to finalise the
OL,15,Fdefence investment plan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776269466
OL,3,CEx Nato chief says UK is
OL,4,C'underprepared, underinsured and under
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FThe Financial Times meanwhile reported
OL,8,Fthat there is a funding gap of around
OL,9,F#28 billion in the existing plans, and
OL,10,Fthe Ministry of Defence, Treasury and
OL,11,FDowning Street are deadlocked over how
OL,12,Fto proceed with the new ten-year plan.
OL,14,FA government spokesman said the review
OL,15,Fwas backed by "the largest sustained
OL,16,Fincrease in defence spending since the
OL,17,FCold War, with a total of over #270
OL,18,Fbillion being invested across this
OL,19,FParliament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776269466
OL,3,CEx Nato chief says UK is
OL,4,C'underprepared, underinsured and under
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,F"We are finalising our defence
OL,8,Finvestment plan that we will publish
OL,9,Fas soon as possible, putting the best
OL,10,Fkit and technology into the hands of
OL,11,Four forces, rebuilding British
OL,12,Findustry to make defence an engine for
OL,13,Fgrowth and doubling down on our own
OL,14,Fcommitment to Nato."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
