OL,3,CEx Nato chief says UK is
OL,4,C'underprepared, underinsured and under
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FSpeaking on Tuesday, Conservative
OL,8,Fleader Kemi Badenoch backed Lord
OL,9,FRobertson's comments, telling BBC
OL,10,FRadio 5 Live: "We used to spend one in
OL,11,Fevery seven pounds on welfare. Now
OL,12,Fit's one in every three pounds, and a
OL,13,Flot of that money has basically been
OL,14,Fswapped for defence.
OL,16,F"The world is not as peaceful as it
OL,17,Fused to be. The peace dividend that
OL,18,Fexisted after the fall of the Berlin
OL,19,FWall is gone; we need to spend more
OL,20,Fmoney on defence."
OL,26,@rD@OOUxD@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776269466
OL,3,CEx Nato chief says UK is
OL,4,C'underprepared, underinsured and under
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FIn a speech delivered on Saturday, she
OL,8,Fpreviously called for the UK to reset
OL,9,Frelations with the US.
OL,11,FBadenoch said some of Mr Trump's
OL,12,Frhetoric had "dismayed" her, but that
OL,13,F"regardless, we must not miss the
OL,14,Funderlying lesson".
OL,16,FShe added: "We must look beyond this
OL,17,Fconflict in the Middle East and
OL,18,Fdevelop the resources we need to
OL,19,Frespond to this new era of threats.
OL,26,@tD@NOUtD@WO]uD@AOUvD@RO]xD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776269466
OL,3,CEx Nato chief says UK is
OL,4,C'underprepared, underinsured and under
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,F"We have a huge amount of work to do
OL,8,Fto reassert Britain as a power in the
OL,9,Fworld.
OL,11,F"First and foremost, we must rearm. If
OL,12,Four military is strengthened, our hand
OL,13,Fis strengthened. We must undertake the
OL,14,Fbiggest peacetime programme of
OL,15,Frearmament in our country's history."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
