PN,31413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776269466
OL,3,CEx Nato chief says UK is
OL,4,C'underprepared, underinsured and under
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FThe Tories have pledged "the largest
OL,8,Fnet increase in British troops under
OL,9,Fany government since the Second World
OL,10,FWar" if they return to power,
OL,11,Fincluding recruiting 6,000 regular
OL,12,Fsoldiers and 14,000 reservists.
OL,14,FThey said some #20 billion could be
OL,15,Ffound to fund the effort by
OL,16,Freinstating the two-child benefit cap
OL,17,Fand reallocating money for Government
OL,18,Fresearch and development and net zero
OL,19,Fprojects.
OL,26,@oD@YOUrD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
